[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_separator color="#999999"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: justify;">As business owners, you want to ensure your future and the future of your family.  Bliss Marc’s 401K and Retirement Planning specialists will help you draw up a plan that allows you to invest in future planning without compromising the present.  We listen to your needs and help you determine contributions that provide a savings that you can count on for the future.</p>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]
